title: Video Learn the Basic Art of Fly Fishing 698MB
description:
Title: Flyfishing

Featuring: Dr. Eric Pettine

Sportsman's Workshop series, Warburton Productions

Length: 51 minutes, 19 seconds

Language: English

Dubbed from VHS tape to DVD disk using separate player and recorder, set to highest quality setting consistent with disk size. Transcoded to Dvix Avi format using Auto GK, target file size 698MB. Audio Stream AC3 Aspect ratio: 4:3 

An instructional flyfishing video including:

"Flyfishing gear and how to use it
Fly casting techniques
How to read the water for best fish catching results
How to catch, fight and land a fish (also how to release)
Safe fishing tips
Fly selection tips
Plus much, much more..."
